            <lg xml:id="TK728">
<l>pallavai kaṟṟum payamilarē nallavaiyu</l>
<l>ṇaṉku celac collātār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who cannot agreeably speak good things before a good assembly are indeed unprofitable persons inspite of all their various acquirements.</l>
